@TicketService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5102
@ApiGateway = http://localhost:5100

### 1. Health Check
GET {{TicketService_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. Utwórz nowy ticket (wymaga auth)
POST {{TicketService_HostAddress}}/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Problem z logowaniem",
  "description": "Nie mogę się zalogować do systemu",
  "priority": "High",
  "category": "Technical"
}

### 3. Pobierz wszystkie tickety (wymaga auth)
GET {{TicketService_HostAddress}}/api/tickets
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Pobierz ticket po ID (wymaga auth)
GET {{TicketService_HostAddress}}/api/tickets/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Aktualizuj ticket (wymaga auth - Agent/Admin)
PUT {{TicketService_HostAddress}}/api/tickets/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Problem z logowaniem - AKTUALIZACJA",
  "description": "Rozwiązane - zresetowano hasło",
  "status": "Resolved",
  "priority": "High"
}

### 6. Usuń ticket (wymaga auth - Admin)
DELETE {{TicketService_HostAddress}}/api/tickets/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### ====== PRZEZ API GATEWAY ======

### 7. Przez Gateway - Utwórz ticket
POST {{ApiGateway}}/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Pytanie o funkcjonalność",
  "description": "Jak dodać nowego użytkownika?",
  "priority": "Medium",
  "category": "Question"
}

### 8. Przez Gateway - Pobierz wszystkie tickety
GET {{ApiGateway}}/api/tickets
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 9. Przez Gateway - Pobierz ticket po ID
GET {{ApiGateway}}/api/tickets/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
